<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[الكِباسة]</span>: العِزْق بشماريخه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>... فَعِيل<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
